be ready to join the battle.

339
00:23:57,050 --> 00:23:57,980
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

340
00:24:01,370 --> 00:24:01,980
Du Bin,

341
00:24:05,050 --> 00:24:06,500
I had someone check the military records.

342
00:24:06,810 --> 00:24:08,700
We don't have anybody named Du Kui here.

343
00:24:11,500 --> 00:24:13,570
