477
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:40,700
How do you know both my name, Du Bingyan,

478
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:42,570
and the name of that girl?

479
00:33:01,090 --> 00:33:04,060
In fact, I know everything.

480
00:33:05,090 --> 00:33:06,700
Miss Du from the Du family in Yangzhou

481
00:33:06,700 --> 00:33:07,570
was supposed to marry

482
00:33:07,570 --> 00:33:09,700
Qi Tianlei
from the Qi Residence in Linzhou.

483
00:33:09,890 --> 00:33:11,130
Meanwhile, Yuan Buqu from Jingzhou

484
00:33:11,130 --> 00:33:12,500
was set to marry

485
00:33:12,980 --> 00:33:15,170
Li Yuhu from the Li Residence in Yangzhou.

486
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:18,370
You two ladies wed on the same day,

487
00:33:18,610 --> 00:33:19,700
rode in bridal sedans together,

488
00:33:20,090 --> 00:33:22,060
and entered the Fairy Temple
at the same time.

489
00:33:22,370 --> 00:33:24,540
You mistakenly took the wrong veils

490
00:33:24,810 --> 00:33:26,300
and ended up in the wrong carriages.

491
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:27,980
Master,

492
00:33:28,570 --> 00:33:30,020
how do you know everything?

493
00:33:32,090 --> 00:33:33,980
Well, I have a knack for fortune-telling.

494
00:33:33,980 --> 00:33:34,940
People call me

495
00:33:35,410 --> 00:33:36,370
Fortuneteller Liu.

496
00:33:38,260 --> 00:33:38,850
Master,

497
00:33:39,500 --> 00:33:40,850
it's truly an honor for me

498
00:33:40,850 --> 00:33:41,980
to become your disciple in this lifetime.

499
00:33:45,650 --> 00:33:46,740
From now on,

500
00:33:47,060 --> 00:33:49,890
I want to learn medicine, swordsmanship,

501
00:33:50,460 --> 00:33:51,300
martial arts,

502
00:33:51,810 --> 00:33:53,610
and foreseeing the future from you.

503
00:33:56,330 --> 00:33:58,500
Sounds like you're planning to learn

504
00:33:58,500 --> 00:33:59,780
all of my lifelong skills.

505
00:34:00,260 --> 00:34:02,060
Even if you're my daughter,

506
00:34:02,060 --> 00:34:04,780
I might not teach you everything.

507
00:34:07,410 --> 00:34:08,130
Well, Master,

508
00:34:08,860 --> 00:34:09,540
what about...

509
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:11,020
What?

510
00:34:11,460 --> 00:34:12,610
Please take me in as your adopted daughter.

511
00:34:12,770 --> 00:34:14,500
I'll be glad
to have a smart adopted daughter like you.

512
00:34:17,170 --> 00:34:17,940
Adoptive Father,

513
00:34:17,940 --> 00:34:19,060
please accept a bow from me.

514
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:22,460
Come on up.

515
00:34:25,820 --> 00:34:26,500
Bingyan,

516
00:34:27,340 --> 00:34:28,250
I'm not

517
00:34:28,250 --> 00:34:29,570
some kind of prodigy.

518
00:34:30,770 --> 00:34:32,290
I came from Linzhou.

519
00:34:33,250 --> 00:34:34,570
The Third Young Master of the Qi family

520
00:34:34,570 --> 00:34:35,980
is also my disciple.

521
00:34:37,210 --> 00:34:38,210
Tianlei is pretending to be sick

522
00:34:38,210 --> 00:34:40,650
to deal with those wicked people
in the mansion.

523
00:34:41,130 --> 00:34:41,690
Right,

524
00:34:42,090 --> 00:34:44,420
Yuhu is incredibly skilled
in martial arts.

525
00:34:45,170 --> 00:34:46,860
Both of them seem to be

526
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:49,290
a match made in heaven.

527
00:34:49,570 --> 00:34:51,900
Fate is inexplicable.

528
00:34:52,690 --> 00:34:54,730
Things took an unexpected turn in Linzhou,

529
00:34:54,730 --> 00:34:56,020
and a fortuitous match was made.

530
00:34:56,420 --> 00:34:58,500
If the two of you could

531
00:34:59,250 --> 00:35:01,210
hit it off in Jingzhou,

532
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:04,540
then you married the right person,

533
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:05,980
although you got into
the wrong bridal sedan.

534
00:35:07,090 --> 00:35:07,980
Master.

535
00:35:08,900 --> 00:35:09,980
Stop calling me Master.

536
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:11,570
Adoptive Father.

537
00:35:12,570 --> 00:35:13,540
Stop making me blush.

538
00:35:16,090 --> 00:35:16,860
Du Bin,

539
00:35:17,090 --> 00:35:18,020
I've been looking for you.

540
00:35:18,290 --> 00:35:20,290
Your strategy was truly brilliant.

541
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:21,540
We managed to defeat

542
00:35:21,540 --> 00:35:22,690
the enemy's cavalry.

543
00:35:23,570 --> 00:35:24,250
Really?

544
00:35:26,090 --> 00:35:26,940
Lieutenant Sha,

545
00:35:27,020 --> 00:35:28,380
tell us about it.

546
00:35:29,060 --> 00:35:29,900
What do you want to know?

547
00:35:30,290 --> 00:35:32,090
The story about the black beans?

548
00:35:32,210 --> 00:35:34,380
Yes. What exactly happened?

549
00:35:34,730 --> 00:35:35,570
Well,

550
00:35:36,250 --> 00:35:37,250
scattering black beans

551
00:35:37,250 --> 00:35:39,090
might sound like a small move.

552
00:35:39,250 --> 00:35:41,980
But it's actually a brilliant strategy.

553
00:35:42,540 --> 00:35:43,460
When the enemy's warhorses

554
00:35:43,460 --> 00:35:45,690
catch a whiff of that black bean aroma,

555
00:35:45,980 --> 00:35:46,980
they all lower their heads

556
00:35:47,250 --> 00:35:48,340
and start searching for beans to munch on.

557
00:35:48,570 --> 00:35:49,570
That's when we strike.

558
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:51,060
Our war drums sounded like thunder

559
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:52,290
as we charged ahead.

560
00:35:52,570 --> 00:35:54,500
The enemy was taken aback,

561
00:35:54,820 --> 00:35:56,570
and their leadership crumbled.

562
00:35:56,980 --> 00:35:58,900
We charge straight into their main camp

563
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:00,730
like slicing through vegetables
with a knife,

564
00:36:00,860 --> 00:36:01,980
and we emerge victorious.

565
00:36:03,090 --> 00:36:04,380
Take a guess.

566
00:36:05,420 --> 00:36:07,020
Who do you think proposed the idea?

567
00:36:08,090 --> 00:36:08,770
Who is it?

